import React from 'react' import { useForm } from "react-hook-form"; import { yupResolver } from "@hookform/resolvers/yup"; export const Form = ({formSchema}) => { const { register, handleSubmit, formState: { errors }, } = useForm({ resolver: yupResolver(formSchema), }); const submit = (data) => console.log(data) return (
{errors.name?.message}
{errors.email?.message}
{errors.password?.message}
{errors.confirmPassword?.message}
{errors.bio?.message}
{errors.contact?.message}
) }
